---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={`About | ${SITE.title}`}
  description="Learn about Trinh Le - Software Engineer at Lazada and creator of Iced Tea Labs"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8 lg:p-12">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Hi there!
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My name is <strong>Trinh Le</strong> - a software engineer who is currently working at 
          <a href="https://www.lazada.vn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover font-medium">@Lazada</a>.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This blog is a space where I share my thoughts on anything (mostly technical, duh!).
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The name "Iced Tea Labs" is inspired by memories of my university time. I was part of a team named "Iced Tea 09" and we participated in many competitions together. That's such a good time though.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I also have a Google Play store also named 
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/dev?id=7059334999797832434" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover font-medium">"Iced Tea Labs"</a> 
          to publish some of my side projects:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Published Apps</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.icetea09.bucketlist" 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <img src="/assets/images/buckist.png" 
                   alt="Buckist app icon" 
                   width="50" 
                   height="50" 
                   class="rounded-lg" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Buckist</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">Best bucket list app</div>
              </div>
            </a>

            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.icedtealabs.mymoney" 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <img src="/assets/images/mymoney.png" 
                   alt="myMoney app icon" 
                   width="50" 
                   height="50" 
                   class="rounded-lg" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">myMoney</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">Expense Manager</div>
              </div>
            </a>

            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.icedtealabs.moon" 
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <img src="https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/fh1U3sqmhbWWRiS6fjh4caslBlE86ZlJBgucayR5wko743aM_U143sHPLTVZvJuHZA=s360-rw" 
                   alt="Moon app icon" 
                   width="50" 
                   height="50" 
                   class="rounded-lg" />
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Moon</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">Blue light filter, night mode</div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm also really really into climbing recently. So there might be some post of me flexing with my climbing skill in the future then. 
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          If you want to find out more about my professional experiences, you can check out my 
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/trinhlbk1991/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover font-medium">linkedin</a> 
          account.
        </p>

        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">Happy coding! ðŸ’»</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
